OL,2,MMountains, Rescues, and Risks
OL,4,CAndrew Godwin
OL,5,CFri 15:00-15:30
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GIt's human nature to ignore or
OL,9,Gdownplay risk until it actually
OL,10,Ghappens - but how do you handle it in
OL,11,Ga high-consequence environment? How do
OL,12,Gyou take a situation that has already
OL,13,Gbeen dangerous for one person and
OL,14,Ginsert ten more safely? For some
OL,15,Greason, groups of people worldwide
OL,16,Gvolunteer to do backcountry rescue -
OL,17,Gin mountains, canyons, deserts, and
OL,18,Gmore. In these hostile environments,
OL,19,Gignoring risk isn't an option; so how
OL,20,Gdo we manage it, embrace it, and work
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
